quran[30]{c,v,t}:
  67,1,"Niwoluyali ulia wobwaami bwoosi buli mumukhono kukwe, naye ni Omunyali muno wabuli eshindu."
  67,2,"Owaloonga lifwa nende obulamu khulwa okhubateema mbu ni wina mwinywe ukhola amalayi muno, naye niye Owaamaani muno, Omunji wobulesheli."
  67,3,"Niye owalonga amakulu saba keyichikhane. Shiwakhalolakhwo mubuloonji bwa Omunji Wetsimbabaasi obwawukhani tawe. Kho kalusiakhwo tsimoni! Olalolakhwo obuleemefu bwosibwosi?"
  67,4,"Mana khandi kalusia tsimoni tsitsio olwakhabili, tsilakhukalushila omwene nitsibeelele, natsio nitsichoonyele."
  67,5,"Ne toto bwene khwarona likulu lieshialo elia hambi nende tsitaa, ne nikhutsikhola okhuba eshikhupo khumashetani, ne khwabarecheshela eshinyasio shiomulilo kwakhanga muno."
  67,6,"Ne balia bakhaya okhuloonda ka Nyasaye wabu Omulesi, balinyoola eshinyasio shia Jahannam, ne ni abundu ambii muno wookhuweera."
  67,7,"Olwa balisukunwamwo, balikuwulila nikuwoola ne nikupupuchila."
  67,8,"Kukhaaba okhukhalikhamwo khulwoburuma. Buli olwa Omukanda kusukunwamwo, abemeresi bakwo babareeba mbu: “Omwikanyilisi shiyabetselakhwo tawe?”"
  67,9,"Baliboola mbu: “Ata, toto bwene abekanyilisi bakhwitsila ne nikhubaingasia, ne nikhuboola mbu: “Nyasaye shiyeshiakhwo shiosishiosi tawe, enywe amukhali butswa mubukori obukhongo.”"
  67,10,"Ne baliboola mbu: “Khubetsanga bokhuwulila nohomba bamachesi, shikhwakhabere mubandu bomulilo tawe.”"
  67,11,"Kho mana balifuchilila tsimbi tsiabu, kho mana babe ale muno abandu bomumulilo."
  67,12,"Toto bwene balia baria Nyasaye wabu Omulesi mukabalalolanga tawe, bali nende obulesheli nende omurungo omukhongo."
  67,13,"Ne lomalome amakhuwa kenywe mumwoyo kwa asi nohomba mumwoyo kwa ekulu, toto Ye amanyile muno akali mubilifu."
  67,14,"Yakhakhaywa okhumanya owaloonga, naye niye omumanyi wamakhuwa kefisile, mwene amakhuwa koosi?"
  67,15,"Niye owabakholela liloba okhuba eliangu khubukhala bwenyu. Kho chendekhwo mutsimbeka tsialio tsioosi, ne lie khumiandu chichie. Ne ewuwe niwamulilamusibwa okhutsia."
  67,16,"Mparanga mbu muli nomulembe okhurulana nende ulia uli hekulu mbu shanyala okhubayibisia muliloba nalio nilirenga tawe?"
  67,17,"Nohomba mparanga mbu muli nomulembe okhurulana nende ulia uli hekulu, mbu shanyala okhubarumila omuyeka kweyimbumbuyeka kwetsimbaale tawe? Ne mulimanya butswa mbu amekanyilisio kanje kali karie."
  67,18,"Ne toto bwene bamala okhukatsula balia bali imbeli wabu, kho mana okhusinyikha khwanje khwali khurie?"
  67,19,"Nohomba shibalolangakhwo amayoni hekulu wabu shingala kabambulanga tsimbaya nende kafumbanga halala tawe? Shakatilililanga tawe halali Omunji Wetsimbabaasi. Toto bwene Ye ni Omuloli muno wabuli eshindu."
  67,20,"Ne ni wina oyo unyala okhuba omukanda kwenyu kwabalwani kwokhubahabina owulali Omuunji wetsimbabaasi tawe? Toto bwene abakhayi shibali khushiosishiosi tawe halali mukhukatania."
  67,21,"Nohomba niwina oyo unyala okhubahelesia omuhandu, Ye niyekalila omuhandu kukwe? Halali abo bahandila sa khubufuru nende okhwira ehale."
  67,22,"Koo, ulia uchendanga niyetukumula nabushila khubweni bwe, nomulunjifu muno nohomba ulia uchendanga shiluunji khunjila ingololofu?"
  67,23,"Boola mbu: “Ye niwabaloonga olwambeli, nabahelesia tsimbulililo nende tsindolelo, nende emioyo. Ne oriomuno yenyu ni inditi muno.”"
  67,24,"Boola mbu: “Ye niye wabasaalasia khushialo, na ewuwe niwa mulikhung’asibwa.”"
  67,25,"Ne baboolanga mbu: “Ni liina kamulakanga kano, nikali mbu muboolanga obwatoto?”"
  67,26,"Boola mbu: “Obumanyi bwe inyanga eyo buli khu Nyasaye, nasi shendi halali omwikanyilisi wa habulafu.”"
  67,27,"Olwa balilola kabalakwa nikakhoola, obweni bwa abakhayi bulisinyikha, ne baliboolelwa mbu: “Kano niko kamwasabaanga muno.”"
  67,28,"Boola mbu: “Mulola murie Nyasaye niyasishia halala nende bali ninasi, nohomba nakhubeela tsimbabaasi, ni wina ulilinda abakhayi okhurulana nende eshinyasio eshilulu?”"
  67,29,"Boola mbu: “Ye niye Omunji wetsimbabaasi, khwamusuubila, ne niye wakhwesika. Ne mulimanya ni wina uli mubukori bulolekha.”"
  67,30,"Boola mbu: “Mulola murie amaatsi kenyu nikakhama, ni wina ulabarerera amaatsi kakhulukusinjia?”"
